{"tid":1906471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社：中日同意押後習近平訪日計劃","createTime":"2020-03-02T03:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T00:08:17.000Z","uid":241764,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10803c277349972e4d6c08dcec521138aaa9c51c","tid":1906471,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"路透社今日（2日）引述消息報道，中國及日本政府鑑於兩國的新型冠狀病毒疫情未解，同意延遲中國國家主席習近平國事訪問日本的計劃，日本首相安倍晉三本周稍後會作正式公布。<br />\n<br />\n共同社則引述消息報道，中日雙方傾向優先應對疫情，日本政府亦忙於處理疫情，希望推遲習近平原定4月訪日的計劃。至於推遲到何時尚未有定案，但預計會押後至東京奧運和殘奧結束的秋季以後。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20200302/s00004/1583113766428/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e8%b7%af%e9%80%8f%e7%a4%be-%e4%b8%ad%e6%97%a5%e5%90%8c%e6%84%8f%e6%8a%bc%e5%be%8c%e7%bf%92%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e8%a8%aa%e6%97%a5%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200302%2Fs00004%2F1583113766428%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25b7%25af%25e9%2580%258f%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%2590%258c%25e6%2584%258f%25e6%258a%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e7%25bf%2592%25e8%25bf%2591%25e5%25b9%25b3%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%2597%25a5%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0ige2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=7d6049c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200302%2Fs00004%2F1583113766428%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25b7%25af%25e9%2580%258f%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%2590%258c%25e6%2584%258f%25e6%258a%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e7%25bf%2592%25e8%25bf%2591%25e5%25b9%25b3%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%2597%25a5%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583&h=420f47f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/a